  "title": "Entry level - Technician / Maintenance Technician [R22107578]",
  "description": "<p><strong>Summary:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Entry level are welcome; on-the-job training will be provided.</li>\n  <li>Good career progression</li>\n  <li>AWS + VB ; 5 days work week</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Perform troubleshooting, servicing, and preventive maintenance on equipment such as aerospace components, marine, and mechanical systems</li>\n  <li>Diagnose mechanical, electrical, and hydraulic issues and carry out effective repairs to restore optimal equipment performance</li>\n  <li>Conduct routine inspections and testing to ensure equipment reliability, safety, and compliance with technical standards</li>\n  <li>Maintain accurate service records and report defects, parts usage, and maintenance activities</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with engineering or technical teams to support equipment upgrades, modifications, and continuous improvement initiatives</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>ITE or equivalent qualification in Electrical, Mechanical, Building Services, or Engineering.</li>\n  <li>Relevant hands on experience in assembly/ reparing/ maintenance will be added advantage.</li>\n  <li>Entry level are welcome; on-the-job training will be provided.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To Apply, kindly click on the \"<strong>APPLY NOW</strong>\" button</p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Staffking Pte Ltd (20C0358) | Jasmine Wong (R22107578)</strong></p>",
